definitions.definition: A being or entity having no matter or substance .
A thing which is abstract or intangible ; ( uncountable ) chiefly preceded by the : things which are abstract or intangible considered collectively .

main_definition: ( countable , chiefly in the plural ) A being or entity having no matter or substance .
